<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <%- include('partials/head', { 
        title: 'About GadiDrive | Global Automotive Information Hub',
        description: 'Learn about GadiDrive, your trusted global source for automotive information. We provide accurate vehicle specifications, comparisons, and latest news for enthusiasts worldwide.',
        keywords: 'About GadiDrive, automotive platform, vehicle enthusiasts, car specifications, global automotive',
        path: '/about',
        country: null
    }) %>
    
    <style>
    
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-red: #dc2626;
            --card-bg: #111111;
            --border-gray: #374151;
        }
        body { background: #000; color: white; font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; margin: 0; }

        /* Navbar - Left Aligned with Original Style (exactly like index.ejs) */
        .navbar-minimal {
            padding: 1.5rem 0;
        }
        
        .navbar-minimal .logo {
            text-align: left;
        }
        
        .navbar-minimal .logo a {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }
        
        .navbar-minimal .logo span {
            color: #DC2626;
        }

        .custom-title { 
            font-size: 4.5rem; 
            font-weight: 900; 
            text-align: center; 
            letter-spacing: -2px; 
            line-height: 1; 
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem; 
        }
        @media (min-width: 768px) { 
            .custom-title { 
                font-size: 6.5rem; 
            } 
        }
        .custom-title .about { 
            color: white; 
        }
        .custom-title .gadi { 
            color: #dc2626; 
            font-weight: 900; 
        }
        .custom-title .drive { 
            color: white; 
        }

        .about-card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-gray);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 2rem;
            border-left: 5px solid var(--primary-red);
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 2.5rem; 
            font-weight: 800; 
            text-align: center; 
            margin-bottom: 4rem; 
            position: relative; 
            color: white;
        }
        .section-title::after {
            content: ''; 
            position: absolute; 
            bottom: -15px; 
            left: 50%; 
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 100px; 
            height: 4px; 
            background: var(--primary-red); 
            border-radius: 2px;
        }

        /* WHY CHOOSE US - FIXED WITH CSS ICONS */
        .why-item { 
            text-align: center; 
            padding: 2rem 1rem;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .why-icon-container { 
            width: 140px; 
            height: 140px; 
            margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
            position: relative;
        }
        .why-icon-bg {
            width: 100%; 
            height: 100%; 
            background: #f92b2b !important;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex; 
            align-items: center; 
            justify-content: center;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(249, 43, 43, 0.3);
        }
        
        /* Custom Icons using CSS (always visible) */
        .icon-accuracy::before {
            content: "✓";
            font-size: 4rem;
            color: white;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .icon-fast::before {
            content: "⚡";
            font-size: 4rem;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .icon-global::before {
            content: "🌍";
            font-size: 4rem;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .icon-free::before {
            content: "💰";
            font-size: 4rem;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .why-content h4 { 
            font-size: 1.5rem; 
            font-weight: 700; 
            margin-bottom: 1rem; 
            color: white; 
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }
        .why-content p { 
            color: #d1d5db; 
            line-height: 1.6; 
            font-size: 1rem; 
            max-width: 300px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        /* SIMPLE MODERN SIGNIN BUTTON */
        .signin-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #DC2626;
            color: white;
            padding: 1rem 3rem;
            border-radius: 40px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: none;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        
        .signin-btn:hover { 
            background: #b91c1c;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.25);
        }

        /* Footer - Red with Border Radius and Content (exactly like index.ejs) */
        .footer-red {
            background-color: #DC2626;
            margin-top: 3rem;
            border-top-left-radius: 30px;
            border-top-right-radius: 30px;
            padding: 2rem 0;
        }
        
        .footer-content {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 2rem;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1rem;
        }
        
        .footer-logo {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }
        
        .footer-logo span {
            color: #000000;
        }
        
        .footer-text {
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 1rem;
            text-align: center;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .footer-copyright {
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            opacity: 0.7;
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
        }
        
        .footer-divider {
            width: 100px;
            height: 2px;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            margin: 0.5rem 0;
        }

        /* Mobile View FIX - IMPORTANT */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .custom-title { 
                font-size: 3.5rem; 
            }
            
            .navbar-minimal .logo {
                text-align: center;
            }
            
            /* WHY CHOOSE US - MOBILE FIX */
            .why-item {
                padding: 1.5rem 0.5rem;
                margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            }
            
            .why-icon-container { 
                width: 120px !important; 
                height: 120px !important;
                margin-bottom: 1rem;
            }
            
            .why-icon-bg {
                background: #f92b2b !important;
                width: 100%;
                height: 100%;
                display: flex !important;
                align-items: center !important;
                justify-content: center !important;
            }
            
            .icon-accuracy::before,
            .icon-fast::before,
            .icon-global::before,
            .icon-free::before {
                font-size: 3rem !important;
            }
            
            .why-content h4 {
                font-size: 1.3rem;
            }
            
            .why-content p {
                font-size: 0.95rem;
                max-width: 280px;
            }
            
            .section-title { 
                font-size: 2rem; 
                margin-bottom: 3rem;
            }
            
            /* Signin button mobile adjustment */
            .signin-btn {
                padding: 0.9rem 2.5rem;
                font-size: 1.1rem;
            }
            
            /* Grid adjustment for mobile */
            .grid-cols-4 {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(1, 1fr) !important;
                gap: 2rem !important;
            }
            
            .footer-content {
                padding: 0 1rem;
            }
            
            .footer-logo {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }
        }

        /* Tablet View */
        @media (min-width: 769px) and (max-width: 1024px) {
            .why-icon-container { 
                width: 130px; 
                height: 130px; 
            }
            .icon-accuracy::before,
            .icon-fast::before,
            .icon-global::before,
            .icon-free::before {
                font-size: 3.5rem; 
            }
        }

        .contact-item i { 
            font-size: 2.5rem; 
            color: var(--primary-red); 
        }
        .contact-item a { 
            color: #9ca3af; 
            text-decoration: none; 
        }
        .contact-item a:hover { 
            color: var(--primary-red); 
        }
        
        /* Fix for grid layout */
        .grid-cols-3 {
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .grid-cols-3 {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen flex flex-col" style="background-color: #000000;">

    <!-- Navbar - Left Aligned with Original Style (exactly like index.ejs) -->
    <nav class="navbar-minimal">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
            <div class="logo">
                <a href="/">
                    Gadi<span>Drive</span>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="flex-grow container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-8 sm:py-12 max-w-7xl">

        <!-- Hero -->
        <section class="text-center py-12 sm:py-16 mb-8 sm:mb-10">
            <h1 class="custom-title">
                <span class="about">About</span> <span class="text-red-600">Gadi</span><span class="drive">Drive</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-400 max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed px-4">
                Your Global Gateway to Automotive Information — Built for Vehicle Enthusiasts Worldwide
            </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Our Story -->
        <section id="our-story" class="mb-8 sm:mb-10">
            <h2 class="section-title">Our Story</h2>
            <div class="about-card max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center">
                <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-300">
                    Founded by a team of passionate car and bike enthusiasts, <strong class="text-red-500">GadiDrive</strong> started with one goal: 
                    to create a clean, fast, and reliable global platform for vehicle information — without confusing ads or outdated data.
                </p>
                <p class="mt-6 text-gray-400">
                    Today, we're proud to be a trusted source for automotive information worldwide, helping thousands of enthusiasts make better vehicle choices every day.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Mission & Vision -->
        <section class="mb-8 sm:mb-10">
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 sm:gap-12">
                <div class="about-card">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-6 flex items-center gap-4">
                        <span class="text-red-600 text-3xl sm:text-4xl">🎯</span> Our Mission
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                        To empower every vehicle enthusiast with accurate, up-to-date information — through detailed specifications, fair comparisons, and the latest industry news from around the world.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="about-card">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-6 flex items-center gap-4" id="vision">
                        <span class="text-red-600 text-3xl sm:text-4xl">👁️</span> Our Vision
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                        To become the world's most trusted name in automotive information, connecting enthusiasts with the data they need to make confident decisions.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- What We Offer - GLOBAL CONTENT -->
        <section id="services" class="mb-8 sm:mb-10">
            <h2 class="section-title">What We Offer</h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 sm:gap-8">
                <div class="about-card text-center">
                    <div class="text-red-600 text-5xl mb-6">🚗</div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Detailed Specifications</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400">Complete technical details, features, and pricing for vehicle models from multiple countries.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="about-card text-center">
                    <div class="text-red-600 text-5xl mb-6">⚖️</div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Easy Comparison</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400">Compare any two vehicles side-by-side with our powerful comparison tool.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="about-card text-center">
                    <div class="text-red-600 text-5xl mb-6">📰</div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Latest News & Updates</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400">New launches, price changes, industry news, and automotive trends from around the world.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Why Choose GadiDrive - GLOBAL CONTENT (4 items) -->
        <section class="mb-8 sm:mb-10 py-8 sm:py-10">
            <h2 class="section-title">Why Choose GadiDrive?</h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 sm:gap-8 lg:gap-12 max-w-7xl mx-auto">

                <!-- 1. Accuracy -->
                <div class="why-item">
                    <div class="why-icon-container">
                        <div class="why-icon-bg icon-accuracy"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="why-content">
                        <h4>Highly Accurate</h4>
                        <p>We verify every spec to ensure you get the most reliable data from trusted sources.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 2. Fast -->
                <div class="why-item">
                    <div class="why-icon-container">
                        <div class="why-icon-bg icon-fast"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="why-content">
                        <h4>Lightning Fast</h4>
                        <p>Optimized for speed on any device, anywhere in the world.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 3. Global Coverage -->
                <div class="why-item">  
                    <div class="why-icon-container">
                        <div class="why-icon-bg icon-global"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="why-content">
                        <h4>Global Coverage</h4>
                        <p>Information from multiple countries with local prices, specs, and regional details.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 4. Completely Free -->
                <div class="why-item">  
                    <div class="why-icon-container">
                        <div class="why-icon-bg icon-free"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="why-content">
                        <h4>Completely Free</h4>
                        <p>No login, no paywall — everything is 100% free forever for everyone.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Contact, Privacy, Terms, Sign In -->
        <section id="contact" class="mb-8 sm:mb-10">
            <h2 class="section-title">Get In Touch</h2>
            <div class="about-card max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 sm:gap-8">
                    <div class="contact-item">
                        <span class="text-red-600 text-4xl">✉️</span>
                        <p class="font-semibold mt-2">Email</p>
                        <a href="mailto:info@gadidrive.com" class="text-sm sm:text-base">info@gadidrive.com</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="contact-item">
                        <span class="text-red-600 text-4xl">📞</span>
                        <p class="font-semibold mt-2">Phone</p>
                        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm sm:text-base">Coming soon</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="contact-item">
                        <span class="text-red-600 text-4xl">📍</span>
                        <p class="font-semibold mt-2">Location</p>
                        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm sm:text-base">Global</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="privacy" class="mb-8 sm:mb-10">
            <div class="about-card">
                <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-6 flex items-center gap-4">
                    <span class="text-red-600 text-4xl">🛡️</span> Privacy Policy
                </h2>
                <p class="text-gray-300">
                    We value your privacy. GadiDrive does not require sign-up and never sells your data. Your information is safe with us.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="terms" class="mb-8 sm:mb-10">
            <div class="about-card">
                <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-6 flex items-center gap-4">
                    <span class="text-red-600 text-4xl">📄</span> Terms of Service
                </h2>
                <p class="text-gray-300">
                    All information is for reference only. Prices and specifications may vary by country, region, and local dealers.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Simple Modern Sign In Button -->
        <div class="text-center my-8 sm:my-10">
            <a href="/signin" class="signin-btn">
                <span>👤</span> Sign In
            </a>
        </div>

    </main>

    <!-- Footer - Red with Border Radius and Content (exactly like index.ejs) -->
    <footer class="footer-red">
        <div class="footer-content">
            <div class="footer-logo">
                Gadi<span>Drive</span>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-divider"></div>
            <div class="footer-text">
                Your Global Gateway to Automotive Information
            </div>
            <div class="footer-copyright">
                © 2026 GadiDrive. All rights reserved.
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script>
        // Smooth scroll for anchor links
        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^="#"]').forEach(a => {
            a.addEventListener('click', e => {
                const href = a.getAttribute('href');
                if (href.startsWith('#')) { 
                    e.preventDefault(); 
                    const target = document.querySelector(href);
                    if (target) {
                        target.scrollIntoView({behavior: 'smooth'});
                    }
                }
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>